tyle=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Dung t\u00edch: 150ml<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u00e1 tham kh\u1ea3o: 420.000 VND<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4370\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4370\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4370\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-2.webp\" alt=\"T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn GSC 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/59-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4370\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">T\u1ea1i sao n\u00ean ch\u1ecdn GSC 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1ed9 pH chu\u1ea9n 5.5 \u2013 gi\u1eef c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean nh\u01b0 tr\u00e0 xanh, l\u00f4 h\u1ed9i, c\u00e1m g\u1ea1o, h\u1ea1t \u00fd d\u0129<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u, kh\u00f4ng paraben<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f4 c\u0103ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam, ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da y\u1ebfu, da \u0111ang treatment<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p: Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da m\u1ee5n, da \u0111ang ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i sau peel\/laser<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: GSC+ 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel l\u00e0 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c nh\u1eb9 d\u1ecbu, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh. S\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9 pH gi\u00fap duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh, kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m m\u1ea5t l\u1edbp lipid t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, th\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng h\u1eb1ng ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cetaphil-gentle-skin-cleanser-%e2%80%93-huyen-thoai-cho-lan-da-nhay-cam\"><\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><strong>Cetaphil Gentle Skin Cleanser<\/strong> \u2013 Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i cho l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0Xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9: Canada<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Dung t\u00edch: 125ml \u2013 500ml<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> Gi\u00e1 tham kh\u1ea3o: 150.000 \u2013 350.000 VND<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o b\u1ecdt, kh\u00f4ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u, c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc ho\u1eb7c lau kh\u00f4 b\u1eb1ng b\u00f4ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\