kh\u00f4 bong tr\u00f3c<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u00f2ng s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf chuy\u00ean bi\u1ec7t cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. Kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o b\u1ecdt nh\u01b0ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch t\u1ed1t, da sau khi d\u00f9ng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"simple-kind-to-skin-refreshing-facial-wash-gel-%e2%80%93-diu-nhe-va-lanh-tinh\"><\/span><b>Simple Kind to Skin Refreshing Facial Wash Gel &#8211; D\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 v\u00e0 l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9: Anh Qu\u1ed1c<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Dung t\u00edch: 150ml<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u00e1 tham kh\u1ea3o: 120.000 &#8211; 160.000 VND<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4358\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4358\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4358\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/60-3.webp\" alt=\"Simple Kind to Skin Refreshing Facial Wash Gel\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/60-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/60-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/60-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/60-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4358\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Simple Kind to Skin Refreshing Facial Wash Gel<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u, ph\u1ea9m m\u00e0u hay c\u1ed3n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">B\u1ed5 sung pro-vitamin B5 v\u00e0 vitamin E h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i da<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y kh\u00f4 da<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u0103ng, d\u1ec5 mua t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c si\u00eau th\u1ecb v\u00e0 c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p: Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, da d\u1ea7u nh\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p thi\u00ean d\u1ea7u<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: V\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 d\u1ec5 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u1ea3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n an to\u00e0n, Simple l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n sinh vi\u00ean ho\u1eb7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u0103m s\u00f3c da. Tuy nhi\u00ean, k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u gel c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u01a1i \u201cl\u00e0nh t\u00ednh\u201d v\u1edbi da nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea7u ho\u1eb7c trang \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1eadm.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"avene-extremely-gentle-cleanser-lotion-%e2%80%93-lam-diu-da-kich-ung\"><\/span><b>Avene Extremely Gentle Cleanser Lotion &#8211; L\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da k\u00edch \u1ee9ng<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9: Ph\u00e1p<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Dung t\u00edch: 200ml<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Gi\u00e1 tham kh\u1ea3o: 450.000 \u2013 520.000 VND<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u01afu \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4359\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4359\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4359\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/60-4.webp\" alt=\"Avene Extremely Gentle Cleanser Lotion\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/60-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/60-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/60-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/60-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4359\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Avene Extremely Gentle Cleanser Lotion<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee9a n\u01b0\u1edbc kho\u00e1ng Avene n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 ch\u1ed1ng k\u00edch \u1ee9ng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n r\u1eeda l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u2013 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi da b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ho\u1eb7c sau can thi\u1ec7p da li\u1ec5u<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a ch\u1ea5t b\u1ea3o qu\u1ea3n, kh\u00f4ng paraben, kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed3n<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea1ng lotion nh\u1eb9, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y nh\u1eddn r\u00edt<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p: Da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m n\u1eb7ng, da sau peel, laser, da \u0111ang \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t &#8220;n\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t y t\u1ebf&#8221;, l\u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng cho l\u00e0n da c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh kh\u00e1 cao v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch m\u1ea1nh.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-luan\"><\/span><b>K\u1ebft lu\u1eadn:\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m ri\u00eang, do \u0111\u00f3, l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t c\u1ea7n d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m v\u00e0 c\u00e1c y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng, nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u1eeba l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3, v\u1eeba b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng r\u00e0o t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean c\u1ee7a da, GSC+ 5.5 pH Cleansing Gel l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m. V\u1edbi c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea1t chu\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ed9 pH an to\u00e0n, chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng d\u1ea7u n\u01b0\u1edbc, s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng lo k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng GSC \u0111i\u1ec3m qua top 5 s\u1eefa r\u1eeda m\u1eb7t cho da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da \u201ckh\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u\u201d n\u00e0y nh\u00e9!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":7,"featured_media":4357,"comme